The Zondo Commission will continue to hear Eskom-related evidence. JOHANNESBURG - The State Capture Inquiry will continue to hear Eskom-related evidence from former Public Enterprises Minister Lynne Brown. The Zondo Commission will also hear evidence from former Eskom Head of Legal and Company Secretary, Suzanne Daniels. WATCH: State Capture Inquiry hears Eskom related evidence Minister of Mineral Resources, Gwede Mantashe and former Deputy Minister of Justice and Correctional Services, Thabang Makwetla are also expected to give Bosasa related evidence in the evening.